Welcome to Danebook, <%= "#{@user.first_name}" %>!

Thank you for signing up for Danebook. Danebook is a social networking app for Danish students.

-Build your friends' list so you can see what your friends are up to.
-Posts your thoughts so your friends know what's new with you.
-Upload your photos to share.

Visit your own page <%= link_to "here", user_url(@user) %> or consider adding some of your fellow Danes to your friends' list:

<% User.all.shuffle[0..2].each do |friend_candidate| %>
  <%= image_tag friend_candidate.profile.photo.photo.url(:medium) if friend_candidate.profile.photo %>
  <%= link_to friend_candidate.name, user_url(friend_candidate) %>
<% end %>
